---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Contact Endeavor Agency - Start Your Executive Search"
  description="Ready to find your next executive leader? Contact Endeavor Agency today to discuss your leadership needs and start your executive search journey."
>
  <Header />
  
  <main class="pt-20">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-700 text-white">
      <div class="container-custom text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 animate-fade-in">
          Let's Start a <span class="text-accent-400">Conversation</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl opacity-90 max-w-3xl mx-auto animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
          Ready to transform your leadership team? We're here to help you find exceptional leaders who will drive your organization's success. Reach out today to begin your executive search journey.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Contact Form & Info -->
    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
          <!-- Contact Form -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">Get In Touch</h2>
            <form class="space-y-6" action="#" method="POST">
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                <div>
                  <label for="firstName" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">First Name *</label>
                  <input 
                    type="text" 
                    id="firstName" 
                    name="firstName" 
                    required
                    class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all"
                  />
                </div>
                <div>
                  <label for="lastName" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Last Name *</label>
                  <input 
                    type="text" 
                    id="lastName" 
                    name="lastName" 
                    required
                    class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Email Address *</label>
                <input 
                  type="email" 
                  id="email" 
                  name="email" 
                  required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all"
                />
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <label for="phone" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Phone Number</label>
                <input 
                  type="tel" 
                  id="phone" 
                  name="phone" 
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all"
                />
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <label for="company" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Company *</label>
                <input 
                  type="text" 
                  id="company" 
                  name="company" 
                  required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all"
                />
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <label for="title" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Your Title</label>
                <input 
                  type="text" 
                  id="title" 
                  name="title" 
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all"
                />
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <label for="service" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Service Interest</label>
                <select 
                  id="service" 
                  name="service" 
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all"
                >
                  <option value="">Select a service</option>
                  <option value="executive-search">Executive Search</option>
                  <option value="leadership-assessment">Leadership Assessment</option>
                  <option value="succession-planning">Succession Planning</option>
                  <option value="board-search">Board Search</option>
                  <option value="talent-strategy">Talent Strategy Consulting</option>
                  <option value="market-intelligence">Market Intelligence</option>
                  <option value="other">Other</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <label for="urgency" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Timeline</label>
                <select 
                  id="urgency" 
                  name="urgency" 
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all"
                >
                  <option value="">Select timeline</option>
                  <option value="immediate">Immediate (within 30 days)</option>
                  <option value="short-term">Short-term (1-3 months)</option>
                  <option value="medium-term">Medium-term (3-6 months)</option>
                  <option value="long-term">Long-term (6+ months)</option>
                  <option value="planning">Just planning ahead</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Tell us about your needs *</label>
                <textarea 
                  id="message" 
                  name="message" 
                  rows="5" 
                  required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-transparent transition-all"
                  placeholder="Please describe the role you're looking to fill, your organization, and any specific requirements or challenges..."
                ></textarea>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <input 
                  type="checkbox" 
                  id="privacy" 
                  name="privacy" 
                  required
                  class="mt-1 w-4 h-4 text-primary-500 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-primary-500"
                />
                <label for="privacy" class="text-sm text-gray-600">
                  I agree to the <a href="/privacy" class="text-primary-500 hover:text-primary-700">Privacy Policy</a> and consent to being contacted about my inquiry.
                </label>
              </div>
              
              <button type="submit" class="w-full btn-secondary text-lg py-4">
                Send Message
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Contact Information -->
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8">Contact Information</h2>
              
              <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1">Email</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">info@endeavorexecutive.com</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">We typically respond within 24 hours</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1">Phone</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">(555) 123-4567</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Monday - Friday: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM EST</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                  <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path>
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-1">Office</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">New York, NY</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">Serving clients nationwide</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Quick Response Promise -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-primary-100 rounded-2xl p-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Our Response Promise</h3>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Initial response within 24 hours</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Detailed consultation within 48 hours</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Proposal delivered within 1 week</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Schedule Consultation CTA -->
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-700 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Schedule a Consultation</h3>
              <p class="mb-6 opacity-90">
                Prefer to speak directly? Schedule a complimentary 30-minute consultation to discuss your leadership needs.
              </p>
              <a href="#" class="bg-white text-primary-700 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 inline-block">
                Schedule Now
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="section-padding bg-gray-50">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
            Frequently Asked <span class="text-gradient">Questions</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Get answers to common questions about our executive search process and services.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">How long does a typical executive search take?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Most executive searches are completed within 8-12 weeks, though this can vary based on the role complexity, market conditions, and specific requirements. We provide regular updates throughout the process and work efficiently to meet your timeline needs.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">What is your fee structure?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Our fees are typically structured as a percentage of the first-year total compensation for the placed executive. We also offer retained search arrangements with milestone-based payments. We'll provide a detailed proposal outlining all fees and terms during our initial consultation.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Do you provide a guarantee on your placements?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Yes, we stand behind our work with a comprehensive guarantee. If a placed executive leaves within the first 12 months for performance-related reasons, we will conduct a replacement search at no additional fee. Terms and conditions apply, which we'll discuss during our engagement.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">What industries do you specialize in?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              We have deep expertise across technology, healthcare, financial services, manufacturing, and professional services. Our team includes partners with specialized industry knowledge, ensuring we understand the unique challenges and requirements of your sector.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">How do you ensure candidate quality and cultural fit?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Our rigorous assessment process includes comprehensive behavioral interviews, leadership assessments, cultural fit evaluation, and thorough reference checks. We also conduct in-depth discovery sessions with your team to understand your organizational culture and specific requirements.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Can you help with board searches and succession planning?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Absolutely. We specialize in board director searches and comprehensive succession planning services. Our team has extensive experience in governance matters and can help you build effective boards and develop robust succession plans for critical leadership roles.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>